Description_lang: The Coaglamation slams the ground knocking players back and releasing orbs of congealed black blood from canisters throughout the arena that travel towards it. Orbs of black blood that reach The Coaglamation are absorbed, restoring $441222s1% of its maximum health.Players that touch orbs of black blood absorb them and are afflicted with $@spellname442285. $?diff23|diff8[Absorbing an orb creates a pool of black blood at its location, inflicting $459961s2 Shadow damage to all players within the pool and reduces their movement speed by $445435s1%.][]
